%^CYAN%^NAME%^RESET%^

rend - detach limbs from corpse

%^CYAN%^SYNTAX%^RESET%^

rend %^ORANGE%^%^ULINE%^LIMB%^RESET%^ from %^ORANGE%^%^ULINE%^CORPSE%^RESET%^

%^CYAN%^DESCRIPTION%^RESET%^

This will "rend" the limb from the corpse in question. removing the limb from the corpse and giving it to you as a grizzly prize, or proof of deed. Command <corpselimbs> will allow you to find out what limbs are valid.

%^CYAN%^SEE ALSO%^RESET%^

forage, hunt, corpselimbs, hp, score

Syntax: rend <limb name> from <corpse>
